Ah well, my thoughts...<br>
<br>
Towards the end of a session, if the Cleric hasn't been looting I generally toss the Cleric a number of dots that seems about as many as were spent symboling (or Aego, or Virtue). <br>
<br>
As far as other loot, (when I get my way) item drops are rolled between people who would wear them immediately, and rolled between everyone who feels like making a plat if noone could use. Parchments get rolled on by hybrids and casters... though I have, recently, seen a number of casters pass on Ethereals simply because they have all their 61-62 spells.<br>
<br>
As far as cash loot... umm, what is that anyway? Oh right, something you get before you fight in the planes... <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
